<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/7.0.0/css/all.min.css"
      integrity="sha512-DxV+EoADOkOygM4IR9yXP8Sb2qwgidEmeqAEmDKIOfPRQZOWbXCzLC6vjbZyy0vPisbH2SyW27+ddLVCN+OMzQ=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/utilities.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />

    <title>Document</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- top navebar -->
    <section class="nave-bar">
      <div class="container sm flex">
        <img class="" src="/assets/google.png" alt="" height="30px" />

        <div class="search flex">
          <i class="fa fa-search"></i>
          <input type="text" name="search" placeholder="Search" />
        </div>

        <div class="action">
          <ul class="flex">
            <li>
              <a href=""
                >Create <i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i
              ></a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href=""><i class="fa fa-bell" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="profile flex">
          <i class="fa fa-user-circle fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- main -->

    <section class="main">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="post">
          <div class="personal-p flex">
            <a href=""
              ><div class="profile-pic">
                <!-- <img class="" src="/assets/google.png" alt="" /> -->
              </div></a
            >
            <a href=""><p style="font-size: medium">Alex Khatri</p></a>
          </div>

          <h4 class="sm-x">
            [HIRING] Hiring Part-Time Customer Service Support – $3,000/Month –
            Remote
          </h4>
          <p class="sm-x">
            I’m looking for reliable and friendly part-time Customer Service
            Support Representatives to join our growing team. This role is
            remote, so you can work from anywhere — as long as you’re based in
            one of these countries: USA | UK | France | Germany | Canada | Spain
            Position Details: • Salary: $3,000 USD/month • Type: Part-time
            (flexible hours, ~20 hrs/week) • Location: Remote, but must reside
            in one of the listed countries • Start Date: ASAP Responsibilities:
            • Respond to customer inquiries via email, chat, and/or phone •
            Assist with order tracking, product questions, and basic
            troubleshooting • Maintain a friendly and professional tone at all
            times Requirements: • Strong written and verbal communication skills
            in English (other languages are a plus) • Reliable internet
            connection. You can comment here or send a DM, no previous
            experience required.
          </p>
          <div class="function flex">
            <a href=""
              ><i class="fa fa-thumbs-up" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>1</span></a
            >

            <a href=""
              ><i class="fa fa-thumbs-down" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>1</span></a
            >

            <a href=""
              ><i class="fa fa-comment" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>1</span></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
